===Etymology===
From Arabic {{ARchar|[[حجب]]}} (''ħájaba'', 'to veil,' 'to cover,' 'to screen').

===Noun===
'''hijab'''

#''(Islam)'' the [[practice]], when beyond the [[age]] of [[puberty]], of [[dressing]] [[modest]]ly (especially for [[women]]).
# the [[hajib]] [[headscarf]].

